T1  - The ambitious entrepreneur: High growth strategies of women-owned enterprises
AU  - Gundry, Lisa K
AU  - Welsch, Harold P
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 16
IS  - 5
SP  - 453
EP  - 470
PY  - 2001
DA  - 2001/09/01/
