T1  - Age, order of entry, strategic orientation, and organizational performance
AU  - Durand, Rodolphe
AU  - Coeurderoy, Régis
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 16
IS  - 5
SP  - 471
EP  - 494
PY  - 2001
DA  - 2001/09/01/
